message.content: cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.STAT, cs.NEURON - The paper presents a novel approach for constrained Bayesian inference applied to multitask learning and parameter estimation in high dimensional functional neuroimaging. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), statistics (cs.STAT), and neuroscience (cs.NEURON).
